  <summary date="2024-01-24T23:06:51Z" status="Introduced in House">Support Faculty and Expand Access to Nursing School Act of 2023

This bill requires the Department of Health and Human Services to award grants to nursing schools with shortages of nursing faculty or clinical preceptors (nurses who supervise nursing students during clinical rotations) for efforts to recruit and retain those positions.</summary>
